Tshegofatso Ketshabile, nke a maara dịka Tshego bụ onye na-agụ egwu na onye na-ede egwu na South Africa
Ọ ghọrọ onye a ma ama na 2016, mgbe ọ wepụtara egwu ya "Hennessy" ma wepụta abọm izizi ya PinkPanther (2019).

A mụrụ Tshego n'aka ndị ụkọchukwu abụọ e chiri echi na 21 Mee 1990 na Atlanta, Georgia United States ebe ndị mụrụ ya na-agụ akwụkwọ. Ọ na-eme njem nleta gaa South Africa ugboro ugboro site na mgbe ọ dị afọ anọ ruo mgbe ọ mechara kwaga Mafikeng iji lekwasị anya n'ọrụ egwu ya.
Na Mee 2020, Tshego bịanyere aka na nkwekọrịta ndekọ na Def Jam Africa, flagship nke Def Jam Recordings.
Tshego kwetara na ọ bụ onye ọgwụ ọjọọ riri ahụ na 2016. Tshego nwere nwa nwanyị amụrụ na 12 Julaị 2019 na Lola Kyle.
